{"tid":115915,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一國!]學寧波老虎單野，係咩應該告鳩MTR？","createTime":"2017-02-11T02:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T12:13:28.000Z","uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"45fb64a0bb093479767bce88711cba91345f8f07","tid":115915,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>逃票被老虎咬死　家屬要園方負責：不能給人翻進去的機會<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170130/858512.htm?from=fb_et_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170130%2F858512.htm%3Ffrom%3Dfb_et_news&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=375b242b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170130/858512.htm?from=fb_et_news</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2307/d2307289.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2307%2Fd2307289.jpg&h=2866f581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲男子送醫後不治。（圖／翻攝微博，下同。）<br />\n<br />\n大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n浙江寧波一名張姓男子29日為了逃票，翻牆進入雅戈爾動物園，沒想到誤入老虎區，當場被群虎圍攻而死，老虎也在警方救人的過程中被槍殺。今日死者已被帶往山上依家鄉風俗下葬，但他的親戚卻認為園方有疏失，「動物園管理不當，<span style=\"color: red;\">他不能給人翻進去的機會呀，所以要負責任！</span>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2307/d2307288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2307%2Fd2307288.jpg&h=e4ccf51f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n動物園的管理委員會表示，張姓男子當天帶著妻子、兩個孩子和友人一起來動物園，妻子和孩子都有購票入場，但張男和同行友人為了逃票，竟從後方潛入，「<span style=\"color: red;\">他們無視警告標誌，先鑽過一層鐵絲網，然後又翻過一層3公尺高的圍牆</span>，張男先進入老虎區，馬上就被好幾隻老虎圍攻。」<br />\n<br />\n▼男子親戚認為動物園有責任。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p1ee64-8LI0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dp1ee64-8LI0&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=ecb90fe6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p1ee64-8LI0</a><br />\n<br />\n根據《梨視頻》報導，張姓男子的親戚楊先生表示，男子是基層打工者，一個月只賺幾千元人民幣，上有父母、下有兩小兒，家境困難，動物園一定要負責任，「就算他是為了逃票從後面翻牆進去的，那也是動物園管理不當，<span style=\"color: red;\">不能給別人翻進去的機會，你既然有漏洞，別人就會想鑽漏洞呀</span>，所以動物園有責任！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvD3OIaSyyE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIvD3OIaSyyE&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=5c9a2980\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvD3OIaSyyE</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"717f37bda9d09be9c8ff2d1cd284adcd90b616bc","tid":115915,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/11/105233_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F11%2F105233_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f10e5a38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1220ebd60571fdc94fbaa336ecc3fd0116ba7ccc","tid":115915,"uid":32151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"大陸人無恥無極限"},{"pid":"f77ccc486115533c0fa6ac6e32b1a7aa1d6d5443","tid":115915,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T12:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸人無恥無極限</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}